Package AcademicExchangePlatform.model

Class CourseBuilder

java.lang.Object
AcademicExchangePlatform.model.CourseBuilder
public class CourseBuilder extends Object
Builder class for creating Course objects. Provides a fluent interface for setting course properties. Implements the Builder design pattern for constructing Course objects.
